Pick up the brown box from the tan table.

Turn the lamp on that is on the brown side table.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the box and turn the lamp on that is on the brown side table.

Turn on the lamp on the small table in the corner.

high_descs: Turn around, go around the table on the left, turn right, go across the room, turn right, go across the room, turn right and go to the table.
Pick up the box on the table.
Turn around, go toward the fireplace, turn left, go across the room to the table in the corner.
Turn on the lamp on the table.
anns.task_desc: Examine the box by the light of the lamp.
